l":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-06-21T10:08:45Z","updated_at":"2022-06-21T10:08:45Z","body":"I have the same issue. It looks like the issue is introduced with this commit: https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/commit/0286ab3513ade8681a7172c78440a81059435e22\r\nWhen doing a POST request with Javascript and adding the csrf field to the form data I get a 403 (The action you have requested is not allowed.).\r\n\r\nThis problem only happens when using a PHP version lower than 7.3. If I use PHP 7.3 or higher it works fine. \r\nIf I do not use `$config['csrf_regenerate'] = true;` I get only a 403 in Safari (MacOS Monterey). If I set `csrf_regenerate` to `true` I get the error also in Firefox (MacOS Monterey).\r\n\r\n\r\nHow to reproduce?\r\n\r\nCreate an environment with PHP 7.2, and Firefox or Safari on MacOS Monterey.\r\nCreate a new codeigniter project with the following:\r\n\r\n`application/config/config.php`\r\n\r\n```php\r\n$config['cookie_prefix']\t= '';\r\n$config['cookie_domain']\t= '';\r\n$config['cookie_path']\t\t= '/';\r\n$config['cookie_secure']\t= false;\r\n$config['cookie_httponly'] \t= true;\r\n$config['cookie_samesite'] \t= 'Lax';\r\n\r\n$config['csrf_protection'] = true;\r\n$config['csrf_token_name'] = 'csrf_test_name';\r\n$config['csrf_cookie_name'] = 'csrf_cookie_name';\r\n$config['csrf_expire'] = 7200;\r\n$config['csrf_regenerate'] = true;\r\n$config['csrf_exclude_uris'] = array();\r\n```\r\n\r\n`application/controllers/Welcome.php`\r\n\r\n```php\r\npublic function index()\r\n{\r\n\t$this->load->helper('form');\r\n\t$csrf = array(\r\n\t\t'name' => $this->security->get_csrf_token_name(),\r\n\t\t'hash' => $this->security->get_csrf_hash()\r\n\t);\r\n\t$this->load->view('welcome_message', [\r\n\t\t'csrf' => $csrf\r\n\t]);\r\n}\r\n\r\npublic function submit()\r\n{\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n`application/views/welcome_message.php`\r\n```\r\n<script>\r\n\tconst formData = new FormData();\r\n\tformData.append(\"<?=$csrf['name'];?>\", \"<?=$csrf['hash'];?>\");\r\n\r\n\tfetch('welcome/submit', {\r\n\t\tmethod: \"POST\",\r\n\t\tbody: formData\r\n\t});\r\n</script>\r\n```","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/comments/1161540728/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"BitmanNL","id":11459708,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjExNDU5NzA4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11459708?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL","html_url":"https://github.com/BitmanNL","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BitmanNL/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":6880618584,"node_id":"REFE_lADOACIW9s5KfSlTzwAAAAGaHehY","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/events/6880618584","actor":{"login":"khashabawy","id":400698,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQwMDY5OA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/400698?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/khashabawy","html_url":"https://github.com/khashabawy","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/khashabawy/followers","following_url":"https: